rows.label: qst400103_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, Maxim-san! I'd like
to transfer some money...

rows.label: qst400103_msg0002
rows.name:
Well, if it isn't Rex. It's rare for
you to bring the cash in person.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0003
rows.name:
It's a big sum this time, so
Meroro-san told me I should
bring it straight to you.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0004
rows.name:
You're a good man, you know that?
Sending money back to your home
village every single month.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0005
rows.name: Heheh... It's nothing, really.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0006
rows.name: So, how much are you sending?

rows.label: qst400103_msg0007
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] I don't want to send it all... I'll
leave a little for myself...

rows.label: qst400103_msg0008
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]Could you send 90,000G to Auntie
Correl in Iyasaki Village for me?

rows.label: qst400103_msg0009
rows.name:
Whew, that's quite a sum. Did
you pull up some huge treasure?

rows.label: qst400103_msg0010
rows.name:
Something like that. I took on
a big job from the Chairman.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0011
rows.name: Sounds like a pie I'd want a piece of.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0012
rows.name:
Oh, right, I have a delivery for
you too. Glad you stopped by, saved
me the trouble of finding you!

rows.label: qst400103_msg0013
rows.name: It's from that same Auntie Correl.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0014
rows.name: Whoa, Braised Cloud Sea Shark!

rows.label: qst400103_msg0015
rows.name:
Mmm, that looks delicious... I'll
have to dig into that later.

rows.label: qst400103_msg0016
rows.name:
Thanks, Maxim-san. Please take
care of that transfer for me!

rows.label: qst400103_msg0017
rows.name: You can count on me!

rows.label: qst400103_msg0018
rows.name: How much will you send?

rows.label: qst400103_msg0019
rows.name: Send 90,000G

rows.label: qst400103_msg0020
rows.name: Don't send anything yet
